       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. PAYROLL-PROCESSOR.
       AUTHOR. LEGACY-SYSTEMS-INC.
      *----------------------------------------------------------------
      * PAYROLL PROCESSING MODULE - CALCULATES EMPLOYEE PAY
      * LAST MODIFIED: 1998-03-15
      *----------------------------------------------------------------

       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
       FILE-CONTROL.
           SELECT EMPLOYEE-FILE ASSIGN TO "EMP.DAT"
               ORGANIZATION IS SEQUENTIAL.
           SELECT PAYROLL-FILE ASSIGN TO "PAY.DAT"
               ORGANIZATION IS SEQUENTIAL.
           SELECT TAX-TABLE-FILE ASSIGN TO "TAX.DAT"
               ORGANIZATION IS INDEXED
               ACCESS MODE IS RANDOM
               RECORD KEY IS TAX-BRACKET-KEY.

       DATA DIVISION.
       FILE SECTION.
       FD EMPLOYEE-FILE.
       01 EMPLOYEE-RECORD.
           05 EMP-ID           PIC 9(6).
           05 EMP-NAME         PIC X(30).
           05 EMP-HOURLY-RATE  PIC 9(4)V99 COMP-3.
           05 EMP-HOURS-WORKED PIC 9(3)V9  COMP-3.
           05 EMP-DEPARTMENT   PIC X(10).
           05 EMP-TAX-CODE     PIC 9(3).

       FD PAYROLL-FILE.
       01 PAYROLL-RECORD.
           05 PAY-EMP-ID       PIC 9(6).
           05 PAY-GROSS        PIC 9(6)V99 COMP-3.
           05 PAY-TAX          PIC 9(5)V99 COMP-3.
           05 PAY-NET          PIC 9(6)V99 COMP-3.

       FD TAX-TABLE-FILE.
       01 TAX-RECORD.
           05 TAX-BRACKET-KEY  PIC 9(3).
           05 TAX-RATE         PIC V9999   COMP-3.
           05 TAX-THRESHOLD    PIC 9(7)V99 COMP-3.

       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 WS-GROSS-PAY         PIC 9(6)V99 COMP-3 VALUE ZEROS.
       01 WS-OVERTIME-PAY      PIC 9(5)V99 COMP-3 VALUE ZEROS.
       01 WS-TAX-AMOUNT        PIC 9(5)V99 COMP-3 VALUE ZEROS.
       01 WS-NET-PAY           PIC 9(6)V99 COMP-3 VALUE ZEROS.
       01 WS-OVERTIME-HOURS    PIC 9(3)V9  COMP-3 VALUE ZEROS.
       01 WS-REGULAR-HOURS     PIC 9(3)V9  COMP-3 VALUE 40.
       01 WS-OVERTIME-MULT     PIC V9      COMP-3 VALUE 1.5.
       01 WS-EOF-FLAG          PIC X       VALUE 'N'.
       01 WS-ERROR-CODE        PIC 9(3)    VALUE ZEROS.
       01 WS-RECORDS-PROCESSED PIC 9(6)    VALUE ZEROS.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN-PROCEDURE.
           PERFORM OPEN-FILES
           PERFORM PROCESS-EMPLOYEES UNTIL WS-EOF-FLAG = 'Y'
           PERFORM CLOSE-FILES
           STOP RUN.

       OPEN-FILES.
           OPEN INPUT EMPLOYEE-FILE
           OPEN OUTPUT PAYROLL-FILE
           OPEN I-O TAX-TABLE-FILE
           READ EMPLOYEE-FILE AT END MOVE 'Y' TO WS-EOF-FLAG.

       PROCESS-EMPLOYEES.
           PERFORM CALCULATE-GROSS-PAY
           PERFORM LOOKUP-TAX-RATE
           PERFORM CALCULATE-NET-PAY
           PERFORM WRITE-PAYROLL-RECORD
           ADD 1 TO WS-RECORDS-PROCESSED
           READ EMPLOYEE-FILE AT END MOVE 'Y' TO WS-EOF-FLAG.

       CALCULATE-GROSS-PAY.
           IF EMP-HOURS-WORKED > WS-REGULAR-HOURS
               SUBTRACT WS-REGULAR-HOURS FROM EMP-HOURS-WORKED
                   GIVING WS-OVERTIME-HOURS
               MULTIPLY EMP-HOURLY-RATE BY WS-REGULAR-HOURS
                   GIVING WS-GROSS-PAY
               MULTIPLY EMP-HOURLY-RATE BY WS-OVERTIME-MULT
                   GIVING WS-OVERTIME-PAY
               MULTIPLY WS-OVERTIME-PAY BY WS-OVERTIME-HOURS
                   GIVING WS-OVERTIME-PAY
               ADD WS-OVERTIME-PAY TO WS-GROSS-PAY
           ELSE
               MULTIPLY EMP-HOURLY-RATE BY EMP-HOURS-WORKED
                   GIVING WS-GROSS-PAY.

       LOOKUP-TAX-RATE.
           MOVE EMP-TAX-CODE TO TAX-BRACKET-KEY
           READ TAX-TABLE-FILE
               INVALID KEY MOVE ZEROS TO WS-TAX-AMOUNT
               NOT INVALID KEY PERFORM COMPUTE-TAX.

       COMPUTE-TAX.
           IF WS-GROSS-PAY > TAX-THRESHOLD
               SUBTRACT TAX-THRESHOLD FROM WS-GROSS-PAY
                   GIVING WS-TAX-AMOUNT
               MULTIPLY WS-TAX-AMOUNT BY TAX-RATE
                   GIVING WS-TAX-AMOUNT
           ELSE
               MOVE ZEROS TO WS-TAX-AMOUNT.

       CALCULATE-NET-PAY.
           SUBTRACT WS-TAX-AMOUNT FROM WS-GROSS-PAY
               GIVING WS-NET-PAY.

       WRITE-PAYROLL-RECORD.
           MOVE EMP-ID       TO PAY-EMP-ID
           MOVE WS-GROSS-PAY TO PAY-GROSS
           MOVE WS-TAX-AMOUNT TO PAY-TAX
           MOVE WS-NET-PAY   TO PAY-NET
           WRITE PAYROLL-RECORD.

       CLOSE-FILES.
           CLOSE EMPLOYEE-FILE
           CLOSE PAYROLL-FILE
           CLOSE TAX-TABLE-FILE.
